Provides a framework where automatic eligibility is granted with Phil. Guarantee Corp., Phil. Crop Insurance Corp. P C I C, Agricultural Credit and Policy Council ( A C P C ) and other governmental agencies providing services towards risk - mitigation in the agriculture sector.
